descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains 1750 .jpg images of single rotor heilcopters for use in image classification (or however you deem fit).
PROS: All images have been cleaned, cropped, duplicates removed, bad quality removed etc.
CONS: Varying sizes.

I have used this dataset with various other ones to train a VGG-16 and Inception models in flying object detection and discrimination.
title: Helicopter Dataset - Single Rotor Class
subtitle: Normal helicopter styles
